{"tid":2081643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【語重心長】【德國戰線】城堡守衛戰 之 德國其實都有手足","createTime":"2020-06-27T11:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T00:37:15.000Z","uid":138409,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"555c47e314cdf1361f400eec4ae3576b7bb1836d","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:23:44.000Z","msg":"from 石賈墨fb<br />\n石賈墨就係由舊年一直響德國幫手登報、搞聽證會嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Stegermatt/posts/1182823735411355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FStegermatt%2Fposts%2F1182823735411355&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=085ca353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Stegermatt/posts/1182823735411355</a><br />\n<br />\n呢幾個禮拜，好多嘢做，抽啲時間出嚟寫故仔，其實有啲奢侈。不過我覺得，寄情寫作，可能會幫到我解放一下心胸入面少少嘅鬱氣，所以都寫少少咁大把啦。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢，坦白講，自己喺德國做嘅嘢，有幾有用，我唔係唔知。但係有時候人做一樣嘢，唔係淨係睇有無用而做。<br />\n<br />\n投身德國線之後，媒體，記者或者其他學者訪問我，都會問呢個問題：「點解？」標準答案我會講話係「Hilflosigkeit」。<br />\n<br />\n無助。<br />\n<br />\n不過除咗負面嘅情緒會驅動我做嘢之外，更加多嘅係正面嘅情緒。容許我講兩個故仔畀大家聽：<br />\n<br />\n舊年，我都唔記得咗幾時啦，我記得係香港街頭衝突最嚴重嘅日子，由於德國媒體當時接近日日報導，所以好多德國人都知道香港當時嘅形勢係點。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱想同老婆同仔仔出街，已經上緊車嘅時候，一個年事已高嘅老婆婆，一步一步咁走近我地，面上帶住笑容，一路望實我。<br />\n<br />\n望到我都覺得有啲唔自在嘅時候，佢就開口講：「我係你隔離街嘅鄰居，喺報紙度見到你嘅訪問呀！」佢攞出一個File，小心奕奕咁遞畀我。<br />\n<br />\n原來佢見到呢邊地區報紙同我做嘅訪問之後，特登剪低送畀我，話畀我知佢見到我可以爲自己家鄉出一分力，覺得好開心。話遲啲要介紹埋佢老公畀我認識，<span style=\"color: gold;\">細說佢地當年喺東德經歷過嘅黑暗故事。</span><br />\n<br />\n臨走前，佢再講：我地好支持香港人咖！希望香港人可以成功啦！下次你有咩幫手，記得搵我，我年紀咁大，都唔怕極權可以點對付我！<br />\n<br />\n我望住佢慢慢行返屋企，先發覺原來佢老公都喺花園度坐，望實我地屋企門口，見到我地要出街就「飛奔」過嚟畀張剪報我。<br />\n<br />\n我老婆都望住我講：「呢個婆婆真可愛。」<br />\n<br />\n好啦，到第二個故事：<br />\n<br />\n我自己無咩用LinkedIn，所以收到Message，都係會有E-Mail Notification。<br />\n<br />\n我以爲又係啲獵頭公司叫我跳槽，不過睇真啲，佢Message入面一嚟就有講Hongkong呢個字。<br />\n<br />\n我即刻就開個Message出嚟睇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">無錯，呢個Message就係由Pekker先生寫的。大家睇返協會呢個Post，就知道佢係「城堡守衛者」，原來有中資想收購一個鄰近嘅小城市入面一座歷史悠久嘅城堡，並將佢變成貴族學校，佢寫呢個Message，就係希望我可以用我語言上同身份上嘅優勢，同德國人力陳紅色資本同紅色教育嘅危險。<br />\n<br />\n我會幫佢睇中文資料，同德國人講香港論述同中共嘅危險，佢會幫我地寫文，幫我地出聲明。</span><br />\n<br />\n每次同Pekker先生傾完電話，有時候真係有種「在心中」嘅感覺，原來香港人保衛香港，德國人都會保衛自己嘅家園，我地都係對抗中共嘅進逼。估唔到，原來喺德國，都可以搵到「日耳曼手足」，同佢地齊上齊落。<br />\n<br />\n大家成日都鬧「德國」親共，我再講多次，德國呢個國度，唔係屬於德國政府，唔係屬於德國官員，亦都唔係屬於一少部分嘅德國政治人物同商人。<br />\n<br />\n一個民主國家，講到最尾，都係屬於人民。作爲一個追求民主嘅香港人，呢樣嘢我係深信不移。<br />\n<br />\n柒婆We connect呢句參選口號，實情中到應曬棍，唔單止幾百萬香港人俾你一炮過Connect曬，直頭連德國人都可以靠你間接Connect返去香港。<br />\n<br />\n投身德國線，最覺得值回票價嘅時刻，唔係做咩媒體訪問之類嘅工作，而係嗰一霎那覺得，終於同到一個德國人叮一聲，We connect嗰下。<br />\n<br />\n見到老婆婆抖顫咁伸出嗰隻攞住剪報嘅手。<br />\n<br />\n見到演講台下嘅德國人專注望住你，因爲認同，嗰一下嘅點頭。<br />\n<br />\n見到Pekker先生話幫我地寫份聲明，寄出嘅嗰封E-Mail。<br />\n<br />\n最值得其實係呢下。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">佢地唔係可以喺德國呼風喚雨嘅大人物，亦都唔可以直接影響德國對香港嘅政策。但係我覺得，佢地先係德國嘅主人。我呢啲業餘素人，做嘢慢，能力同經驗欠缺，做嘢無可能做得完美，我係有呢個自我反省的，但係有限制，唔代表就唔做，咪由低做起囉。<br />\n<br />\n唔講獨立，香港人要話自己做「香港民族」，首先自己要有意識成爲「香港構成」嘅一部分，有自己嘅身份，有自己嘅定位，有自己嘅論述，有自己嘅國際連結，先會有望見將來嘅可能</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkerinde/posts/173703960849000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkerinde%2Fposts%2F173703960849000&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=9e841718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkerinde/posts/173703960849000</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfDHP3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfDHP3G.jpg&h=dff5f37f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGzTcg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGzTcg2.jpg&h=c5eece6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝Mr. Zsolt Pekker 對香港的支持🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\nDie B&uuml;rgerinitiative Malteserschloss (BIM) in Heitersheim fordert den Erwerb der historischen Immobilie durch die &ouml;ffentliche Hand. Sie m&ouml;chte erreichen, dass das Schloss mit einer Vielfalt von gemeinwohlorientierten Nutzungsarten f&uuml;r die Menschen der Region erschlossen und ins &ouml;ffentliche Leben eingebunden wird. Dem stehen die Pl&auml;ne einer chinesisch-deutschen Investorengruppe entgegen, die das Geb&auml;ude kaufen und dort eine private Eliteschule einrichten will.<br />\n<br />\n位於德國Heitersheim嘅Malterserschloss公民關注協會（B&uuml;rgerinitiative Malteserschloss, BIM）成立目的<br />\n係希望可以促進以公開方式活化歷史建築，令處於Heitersheim嘅城堡可以用多元化嘅方式咁畀當地嘅居民去用，令城堡可以融入佢地嘅公共生活。<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個協會堅拒反對中德合資集團收購Matlerserschloss城堡，並將佢變成一間私人精英學校嘅計劃。</span><br />\n<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n<br />\nBIM share嘅post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Heitersheim2019/posts/806463239884045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHeitersheim2019%2Fposts%2F806463239884045&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=7d873542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Heitersheim2019/posts/806463239884045</a>"},{"pid":"1b1d433bf88de4ace5093b9694bff51eb4c082d0","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0efd84fba6cf42a918fa53dc040c59a0bbb49d2","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"59304865c42753be28ddcba86db93e24e97999c6","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab2a8ab6058bb5f70bb1c70d46cc2516b60e6883","tid":2081643,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=22d1b408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"98be86ebdf9588de4620798a64338f091c167452","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"573790a1ba18c9506eab1d7dd4eeb9774eed21c3","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"98f232fda434c8e192667623cf380f1ca88a6c7d","tid":2081643,"uid":295124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"dd4dd9662da265ea52da8d040a707c334bd7a028","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:29:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b3d9588fdae908c2bb53bc60e3ab4d7f1a07a70b","tid":2081643,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e444ed5aebd6791297a8fa0fdf3167abcf3a8b2f","tid":2081643,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"Dr&uuml;cken Sie bitte!!!"},{"pid":"24d10b338a0a0ac52bf47ff5e1ace3639deaa8ef","tid":2081643,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424cb9cef5cef37a9158eec9cc0f19ebbc01017f","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a25ae9c2d9cce6b01aa2163703a880118e042f06","tid":2081643,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"多謝德國民間手足支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望西方世界更多平民覺醒，知道中国有幾危險，倒迫佢地政府圍毆中国。"},{"pid":"dbee65abf08a476861b4d42036f424d250b1782d","tid":2081643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215f996b4d0b98276d8dadd6cae3df7c1b006c9a","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1654cf86e64e5c3f5a911f346e89aa75df38c3cc","tid":2081643,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"Dr&uuml;ck"},{"pid":"5b366fc1a044249d253397d7fa99df2f4fd3cf78","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5175fb5e983964ba4203c889f8296ad0a445ab36","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78d9ace9d93c6703fd427658ce0fb493fbb63d1f","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ab3fec0b7c4065ac70d4728508c624e27852ad8","tid":2081643,"uid":332713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"多謝手足既努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf5bd63b844c9e94d97c1cc8c5b5e2c497f6764","tid":2081643,"uid":157808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"多謝手足既付出<br />\n無論有冇成果，都咬緊牙關撐落去<br />\n呢個，就係我地既香港"},{"pid":"38aa6880cd2f966234705b27ff488727bb8af70a","tid":2081643,"uid":137990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:40:26.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<br />\npush"},{"pid":"69ec9fc9404d960338f59bcb969a5a17db6e3317","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"16bb6b9648eb5901894570ca1639bae319ff558f","tid":2081643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"push"}]}